data.description: Super cute 1-story home in Miller Ranch is move-in ready!  Featuring a light and bright open floorplan with a living/dining combo that flows into the open island kitchen, complete with breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances and gas cooking, and primary bedroom with full bath hosting a tub, walk-in shower and double sinks. The backyard backs to green space, with no back neighbors, and hosts a covered porch and large lawn. Great location, close to schools, parks, I-10 and shopping.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this your next home, book your personal tour today!
